<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/154490-does-anyone-else-find-this-book-a-little">Does anyone else find this book a little dumbed-down for historical fiction? I&#39;m only on Chapter 2 and I&#39;m losing interest fast...</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_154490'><a id="like_count_community_question_154490" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/154490?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">32 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F10692.The_Historian">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/154490-does-anyone-else-find-this-book-a-little">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/154490-does-anyone-else-find-this-book-a-little">See all 22 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

